03000,"text":"There's a brilliant particles around it."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00054","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":203000,"end_ms":204000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00055","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":204000,"end_ms":207000,"text":"What direction is it from you?"},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00056","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":207000,"end_ms":210000,"text":"It's about at my two o'clock position."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00057","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":210000,"end_ms":215000,"text":"Does that mean it's ahead of you?"},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00058","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":215000,"end_ms":219000,"text":"It's ahead of us, 2 o'clock, slowly doubling."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00059","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":219000,"end_ms":220000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00060","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":220000,"end_ms":221000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00061","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":221000,"end_ms":224000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00062","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":224000,"end_ms":234000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00063","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":234000,"end_ms":239000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00064","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":239000,"end_ms":241000,"text":"Roger."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00065","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-