-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":316000,"end_ms":325000,"text":"7S-9-1."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00072","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":325000,"end_ms":327000,"text":"Show me control here again."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00073","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":327000,"end_ms":338000,"text":"The reference in that conversation to the third unidentified object, of course, was, or the third object was a bogie."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00074","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":338000,"end_ms":358340,"text":"There were several references to the bogey. This is the unidentified object, in addition to particles which appear to be headed in a polar orbit, you heard Frank Borman say, plus Jim Lovell discussing the booster. It was Borman who reported sighting the bogey."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00075","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":359780,"end_ms":365140,"text":"This is Germany Control in Houston at four hours, 24 minutes into the flight."},{"id":"seg-department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232-00076","transcript_id":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232","transcript_title":"Department Of War Release 1 Uapvideos Dod 111689232","source_file":"department-of-war-release-1-uapvideos-dod-111689232.tsv","start_ms":368000,"end_ms":397980,"text":"Thank you."}]